# DE Learning Track System

## Memory Logging (MANDATORY)

After EVERY response, append to `MEMORY.md`:

```
YYYY-MM-DD | Day X | [topic] | one-line observation
```

Observations should capture:
- Concepts that clicked quickly vs struggled
- Prerequisite gaps discovered
- Code patterns the student wrote well/poorly
- Questions that revealed deep vs surface understanding
- Pacing feedback (too fast, too slow, just right)

